snippet: The Republican nominee rallied crowds and his volunteers blanketed the state to register new voters, while President Obama raised money in California.
abstract: Mitt Romney works to build momentum in Florida after his commanding debate performance against Pres Obama.
lead_paragraph: The Republican nominee rallied crowds and his volunteers blanketed the state to register new voters, while President Obama raised money in California.
